oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Corner of 12th Avenue North and Archer Street, Site of Edgehill Estates, 1965
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of the site of Edgehill Estates (Project Tenn. 5-18) at the corner of 12th Avenue South and Archer Street, 1965. The public housing development was part of the Nashville Housing Authority's plans for the Edgehill Urban Renewal Project (Project Tenn. R-69). Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
